                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6476" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MSL-0087</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9943 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">众志成城：抗击疫情“急”中有序</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Unite as one: fight the epidemic in an orderly and &quot;urgent&quot; way</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">田波，赵娇，续文键</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学商学与管理学院</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">后勤保障部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">突发校园疫情；应急管理；PDCA循环；风险管理；2022百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Campus outbreak; Emergency management; PDCA cycle; Risk management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新冠疫情袭来，应急管理的重要性愈发明显。本案例主要描述了JL大学新合并的SG学院面对校园疫情，众志成城共同抗疫，学院针对学生在寝室隔离期间不断出现的问题，迅速调整应急管理措施并有序实施的过程。本案例从辅导员小裴老师的视角，阐述了SG学院面对学生的物资紧缺、心理问题、生活枯燥等一系列难题，办法总比困难多，学院工作人员协调合作、志愿者迅速成团、开展线上心理沟通室、学生互助等措施，应急管理难题一一破解。通过对本案例的学习与思考，使学生认识到应急管理的重要性，帮助学生掌握应急管理的理论基础。通过现实案例教学使学生认识到学习应急管理的必要性，引导学生运用相关理论知识解决应急管理实际问题，为高校应急管理提供可借鉴的经验与启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the outbreak of COVID-19, the importance of emergency management is becoming more and more obvious. This case mainly describes the process in which the newly merged SG College of JL University quickly adjusted emergency management measures and implemented them in an orderly manner in response to the continuous problems of students during dormitory isolation in the face of the campus epidemic. From the perspective of counselor Xiao Pei, this case illustrates that SG college is facing a series of problems such as material shortage, psychological problems and boring life. There are more methods than difficulties. The college staff coordinate and cooperate, volunteers quickly form a group, carry out online psychological communication room, students&#39; mutual assistance and other measures, and solve the problems of emergency management one by one. Through the study and thinking of this case, students can realize the importance of emergency management and help students master the theoretical basis of emergency management. Through practical case teaching, students can realize the necessity of learning emergency management, guide students to use relevant theoretical knowledge to solve practical problems of emergency management, and provide referential experience and Enlightenment for emergency management in Colleges and universities.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《应急管理》、《风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">应急管理与风险管理、危机管理高校应急管理；高校应急管理原则；应急管理的流程；应急处置与救援机制；应急预案；PDCA循环</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
